raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
do social_post(\"val_jason1\")
do social_post(\"mabel_laundry\")
Mabel: Babe!!! 🥺
Mabel: I had the worst day everrrr!
Player: Worst day so far you mean 😄
Mabel: Now's not the time for jokes! 😭
Mabel: I was at the cafeteria and wanted a quick snack
Mabel: But they ran out of the tiny doughnuts that I really like
Mabel: So I got those little custard cups
Mabel: I already don't like custard cause its like all sugar 😑
Player: Aren't doughnuts all sugar too?
Mabel: MOSTLY sugar, it's a big difference 😌
Player: My bad, big difference
Mabel: Duh, anywayy
Mabel: I couldn't get it open and tried to pop it open
Mabel: And it spilled EVERYWHERE!!
Mabel: I was covered in custard 😭 Just like in my nightmare!!
Player: Oh no!
Player: Did you clean it up?
Mabel: I'm about to take a shower to clean it all off
Mabel: I look like a custard monster seriously 👻
- Show me! [#lust]
	set Story.mabel_desire += 1
	Player: Show me!
	Mabel: No heckin' way!!
	Player: Awwh
	Mabel: Trust me babe, you really didn't wanna see it anyway 😝
	Mabel: I look like a total mess
	Mabel: And I'd rather be pretty in your imagination 🥰
- Hurry up and take a shower 😝
	Player: Hurry up and take a shower 😝
	Mabel: 🫡 Roger that HQ
	Mabel: Carrying out mission with haste!
do advance_time(1, 0)
Mabel: Ok all cleaned up 🎀
Mabel: Got the towel around me hehe
do echo_set([\"54\"])
Player: Bet you're looking all cute
Mabel: You bet right 🥰
Mabel: My sleep schedule keeps me young and pretty 😊
Player: As opposed to old? 😀
Mabel: I'd be a total granny if I didn't have my sleep schedule!!
Player: 18 year old grandma!
Mabel: 🤪
Mabel: Need to change to something cozy
Mabel: Tell me about your day while I do that?
do echo_clear()
if Story.black_heart >= 4:
	do social_post(\"ninas_result\")
Mabel: Anything interesting happen?
- Very long and boring class
	Player: Very long and boring class
	Player: Not much happened
- A friend of mine had some fun with this girl [#distrust]
	Player: A friend of mine had some fun with this girl
	Player: It was during class too lol
	Mabel: What do you mean by fun 🤔
	- Like... hook up [#lust]
		set Story.mabel_desire += 1
		Player: Like... hook up
		do echo_set([\"55\"])
		Mabel: You mean like get all kissy and stuff 😳
		Mabel: With a random girl?
		Player: Mhmm
		Mabel: And he was your friend??
		Player: Yeah
		Mabel: And this happened during class???
		Player: Yep
		Mabel: Omg 😵
		Mabel: How did it happen?
		Player: He like slipped her a note during class
		Mabel: That's all it took!?
		Mabel: Okay well I can't even...
		Mabel: Thought: Why am I trying to imagine this even!?
		Mabel: Thought: That's not okay!
		Mabel: Thought: Bad thoughts go away, bad thoughts go away
		Player: Can't what?
		Mabel: 🙂
		do echo_clear()
		Mabel: So you had an interesting day too
		Mabel: That's nice! 🙂
	- They got all cute [#love]
		set Story.mabel_desire -= 1
		Player: They got all cute
		Mabel: Omg like, is she gonna be his girlfriend now?
		Player: Idk maybe 😅
		Mabel: Wow, it feels like anyone can become anyone's girl at anytime 😳
		Mabel: Isn't that kind of scary 😅
		Player: Scary?
		Mabel: Maybe that's the wrong word... frightening? Anyway I'm sure they're happy!
		Mabel: I'm rooting for them 🥳
		Mabel: I loooove love stories
		Mabel: 🤭
		Mabel: They couldn't wait for after class?
		Player: I don't think so
	Mabel: Good for them
Mabel: I have some reading to do for a quiz so
Mabel: Make sure you do your homework too okay!?
Player: Okay mom!
Mabel: I totally would make an awesome mom!
Mabel: I'd scold you for not eating your greens 😌
Player: 😁
do social_post(\"erikas_firsttime\")
Mabel: Alright study time
Player: Good luck!
Mabel: Good night!!
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
